					<outline text="PS: He did a similar &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.chicagotribune.com/media/mp3/2008-03/36769266.mp3&quot;&gt;interview&lt;/a&gt; with the Chicago Tribune." created="Sat, 15 Mar 2008 06:41:23 GMT"/>
