				<outline text="Clinton running for VP?" created="Fri, 07 Mar 2008 01:47:24 GMT">
					<outline text="&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.cbsnews.com/blogs/2008/03/06/politics/fromtheroad/entry3915709.shtml&quot;&gt;Hillary Clinton&lt;/a&gt;: &quot;Look, I have said that Senator McCain will bring a lifetime of experience to the campaign, I will bring a lifetime of experience and Senator Obama will bring a speech that he gave in 2002. I think that is a significant difference.&quot;" created="Fri, 07 Mar 2008 01:47:44 GMT"/>
					<outline text="It's been pointed out &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Keith_Olbermann&quot;&gt;elsewhere&lt;/a&gt; that you say stuff like that if you want the VP nomination, the &lt;i&gt;Republican&lt;/i&gt; VP nomination." created="Fri, 07 Mar 2008 01:47:55 GMT"/>
